wiki.content:
"Come Away with Me" is a song written by Norah Jones for her 2002 debut album Come Away with Me. The song did not chart on the Billboard Hot 100, but it did place number 21 on the US Adult Top 40. It also charted at number two in Canada and number eighty on the UK Singles Chart.
